snippet.title: Forested Super Mario Bros U  - Reveal Trailer
snippet.description:
WillyMaker originally used the idea of this mod to hide his big project, Super Mario Evolution, but after talking it over with him earlier this year, we decided to make this fictional mod a reality!
---------------------------------------------------------------
--Forested SMBU contains--
- 7 brand new levels
- new tilesets
- custom music
- new backgrounds
- and so much more
---------------------------------------------------------------
We are not affiliated with nintendo all characters such as Mario, Luigi and all the others belong to nintendo. We are just fans of the Super Mario franchise.


- My Discord Server: https://discord.gg/pVp5tQF6cQ
